msgstr ""

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:149
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Instellingen"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:163
msgid "Instance"
msgstr "Instance"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:165
msgid "Your Mastodon instance&rsquo;s URL."
msgstr "De URL van je Mastodon-instance."

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:168
msgid "Supported Post Types"
msgstr "Ondersteunde berichttypes"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:179
msgid ""
"Post types for which sharing to Mastodon is possible. (Sharing can still be "
"disabled on a per-post basis.)"
msgstr ""
"Berichttypes die op Mastodon kunnen worden gedeeld. (Delen kan per bericht "
"nog altijd worden uitgeschakeld.)"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:185
#: includes/class-options-handler.php:230
msgid "Authorize Access"
msgstr "Authoriseren"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:201
msgid "Access granted!"
msgstr "Authoriseren gelukt!"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:229
msgid ""
"Authorize WordPress to read and write to your Mastodon timeline in order to "
"enable crossposting."
msgstr ""
"Laat WordPress toe om je Mastodon-tijdlijn te lezen en ernaartoe te "
"schrijven."

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:235
msgid ""
"You&rsquo;ve authorized WordPress to read and write to your Mastodon "
"timeline."
msgstr ""
"Je hebt WordPress toelating gegeven om je Mastodon-tijdlijn te lezen en "
"ernaartoe te schrijven."

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:250
msgid "Revoke Access"
msgstr "Ongedaan maken"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:259
msgid ""
"Something went wrong contacting your Mastodon instance. Please reload this "
"page to try again."
msgstr ""
"Er ging iets mis met het contacteren van je Mastodon-instance. Herlaad deze "
"pagina om het nog eens te proberen."

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:265
msgid "Please fill out and save your Mastodon instance&rsquo;s URL first."
msgstr "Vul alsjeblieft eerst je Mastodon-instance in."

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:271
msgid "Debugging"
msgstr "Debuggen"

#: includes/class-options-handler.php:272
msgid ""
"Below information is not meant to be shared with anyone but may help when "
"troubleshooting issues."
msgstr ""
"Onderstaande informatie hoor je met niemand te delen maar kan helpen met het "
"troubleshooten van problemen."
